snippet.title: Amber Heard is a LIAR, lying in court declaration // #justiceforjohnny
snippet.description:
Here I went through Amber Heard declaration and counted how many times she lied. Half-truths and lies by omission also. I'm kind of surprised since it is a court document to me I wouldn't want to lie in a court document especially with a case this serious. The document is open to the public. Her declaration has some holes in her story. 

I am doing these videos to prove that #Iamnotabot the counterclaim really upset me. Please do not purposely go harassing Amber Heard. Let's fight against domestic violence. 

Please like and subscribe
https://www.change.org/p/dc-entertainment-remove-amber-heard-from-aquaman-2 petition to have her removed from Aquaman 2
